{"tid":2268660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奇蹟！荷蘭高架地鐵衝過頭飛出軌「鯨魚尾巴」驚險接住","createTime":"2020-11-03T03:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T12:38:39.000Z","uid":38539,"like":238,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"4642f1c262e7ea1cf1415d7c2c22680d62b7991c","tid":2268660,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HScczXZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHScczXZ.png&h=947e594e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭斯派克尼瑟市（Spijkenisse）2日凌晨發生地鐵出軌意外，一列地鐵在約10公尺高的高架軌道上衝過頭，導致一整節車廂衝出軌道末端，幸虧被一個鯨魚尾巴雕塑戲劇性地「接住」，整起事件無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n因為是地鐵線上的終點站，因此除了司機以外沒有其他乘客，司機僅受驚嚇而未受傷，但為了預防起見，負責營運的地鐵公司已將司機送往醫院檢查，並著手調查列車故障原因。<br />\n<br />\n該座鯨魚尾巴雕塑於2002年出自荷蘭建築師兼視覺藝術家特魯伊斯（Maarten Struijs）之手。特魯伊斯說，雕塑是模仿鯨魚潛入海中的模樣，自己對此事件也感到十分驚訝，稱這個塑膠製品已經大約有20年歷史，想不到能承載這麼重的東西，沒有立即崩塌。<br />\n<br />\n截自2日上午，工程師等人仍在研究如何在強風中穩定該節出軌車廂並把它移下來。地方安全局發言人高特（Carly Gorter）說，「這很棘手」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2poZZpO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2poZZpO.png&h=b6903397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4984306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4984306&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0Esg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=935db48a\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4984306</a>"},{"pid":"88b1bc86c2a6f5018fefd28880d2cd6f5e4078ed","tid":2268660,"uid":144626,"like":375,"dislike":3,"score":372,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:31:56.000Z","msg":"有佢喇, 當做景點都好"},{"pid":"e999034ce5c99fbf2568a301088a9a7814ea98e1","tid":2268660,"uid":215876,"like":190,"dislike":2,"score":188,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:34:28.000Z","msg":"舊版蜘蛛俠2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f997efb0ddde84c250d0f129b737c4fdf9a11cbf","tid":2268660,"uid":136416,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"88b1bc86c2a6f5018fefd28880d2cd6f5e4078ed","tid":2268660,"uid":144626,"like":375,"dislike":3,"score":372,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:31:56.000Z","msg":"有佢喇, 當做景點都好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"3114d1a5d65b98f6c591aa7f671eedaa5a361aa6","tid":2268660,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":22,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"荷蘭用左支那野？咁都可以出軌"},{"pid":"72e5fc6382f5c6898656986ef80af8c1afbd1ec2","tid":2268660,"uid":42064,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"3114d1a5d65b98f6c591aa7f671eedaa5a361aa6","tid":2268660,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":22,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"荷蘭用左支那野？咁都可以出軌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"睇圖你真係覺得冇人為因素？"},{"pid":"ab0ddfff5190ae6ec7eaf56ae02e9cf9abfb0ebd","tid":2268660,"uid":167509,"like":62,"dislike":4,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:33:23.000Z","msg":"證明舊版蜘蛛俠最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53767c0e9cd2a4f6e37a106187a1606ded8b14a3","tid":2268660,"uid":35930,"like":216,"dislike":2,"score":214,"quote":{"pid":"3114d1a5d65b98f6c591aa7f671eedaa5a361aa6","tid":2268660,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":22,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"荷蘭用左支那野？咁都可以出軌"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"起碼條鯨魚尾唔是支那野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857f5c502c9a83304ee43b0bb74b6dbb0073be6b","tid":2268660,"uid":6556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:50:29.000Z","msg":"塑膠製品？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c021df03210b63fc182ee5d8dc3a31c0e7760978","tid":2268660,"uid":1069,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:52:12.000Z","msg":"又係雕塑又係安全裝置"},{"pid":"ae4deeddb829a68926dd6d386175abb0df5a20bf","tid":2268660,"uid":156936,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T